Original Sin and Its Consequences
 
French workshop (c. 1275)
 
Window Scenes Include (from top):
 
Adam Laments Over Abel (Gen 4:25-26)
 
God Questions Cain (Gen 4:9-16)
 
Cain Kills Abel (Genesis 4:8)
 
God Rejects Cain’s Offering (Gen 4:2-7)
 
The Labors of Adam and Eve (Gen 3:8-21)
 
God Expels Adam and Eve from Paradise (Gen 3:22-24)
 
The Fall (Gen 3:1-19)
 
Scenes Parallel Window on Left